'''法洛四联症'''（{{lang-en|Tetralogy of Fallot}}，[[简写|简写]]：ToF）屬於[[先天性心臟病|先天性心臟缺陷]]<ref name=NIH2011What>{{cite web|title=What Is Tetralogy of Fallot?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/tof/|website=NHLBI|accessdate=2 October 2016|date=1 July 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161004225713/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/tof|archivedate=4 October 2016|df=}}</ref>。出生時的症狀從無症狀到嚴重不等<ref name=Curr2016>{{Cite book |title=Current diagnosis & treatment : pediatrics |author1=Hay, William W. |author2=Levin, Myron J. |author3=Deterding, Robin R. |author4=Abzug, Mark J. |isbn=9780071848541 |edition=Twenty-third |location=New York, NY |oclc=951067614|date=2016-05-02 }}</ref>，之後多半會有[[發紺|發紺]]（皮膚發藍）的症狀（[[青紫婴儿|青紫婴儿]]）<ref name=NIH2011Sym/>。當有此症的嬰兒哭泣或[[排便|排便]]時，他們可能會有急性缺氧發作：皮膚會轉為藍色，有呼吸困難、跛行、偶爾{{link-en|失去意識|unconsciousness}}<ref name=NIH2011Sym/>。其他症狀可能包含[[心雜音|心雜音]]、{{le|杵狀指|finger clubbing}}、[[母乳哺育|吸食母乳]]時容易疲勞<ref name=NIH2011Sym>{{cite web|title=What Are the Signs and Symptoms of Tetralogy of Fallot?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/tof/signs|website=NHLBI|accessdate=2 October 2016|date=1 July 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005191311/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/tof/signs|archivedate=5 October 2016|df=}}</ref>。

==病因及診斷 ==
法洛四联症的病因目前還不清楚<ref name=NIH2011Ca/>。 風險因素包括懷孕時使用酒精，或是孕婦患有[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]、年齡超過40歲或懷孕期間患上[[德國麻疹|德國麻疹]]<ref name=NIH2011Ca/><ref>{{Cite book|title=Pregnancy and congenital heart disease|last=|first=|date=2017|publisher=Springer|others=Roos-Hesselink, Jolien W., Johnson, Mark R.|isbn=9783319389134|location=Cham|pages=62|oclc=969644876}}</ref>，它也可能與[[唐氏症候群|唐氏症候群]]有關<ref name=NIH2011Ca>{{cite web|title=What Causes Tetralogy of Fallot?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/tof/causes|website=NHLBI|accessdate=2 October 2016|date=1 July 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005191259/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/tof/causes|archivedate=5 October 2016|df=}}</ref>。一般會有四種缺陷<ref name=NIH2011What/>：
* {{link-en|肺動脈狹窄|pulmonary stenosis}}：是右心室出口狹窄。
* [[心室中膈缺損|心室中膈缺損]]：左右心室之間有一個破洞。
* [[右心室肥大|右心室肥大]]：右心室肌肉增厚。
* [[主动脉骑跨|主動脈跨位]]：是兩個心室中的血液皆可進入主動脈。

== 治療及預後 ==
法洛氏四重症通常於一歲時進行[[心脏外科|開心手術]]<ref name=NIH2011Tx/>，手術的時間取決於嬰兒的症狀與體型<ref name=NIH2011Tx/>，過程涵蓋增加{{link-en|肺動脈瓣|pulmonary valve}}和[[肺動脈|肺動脈]]的大小並修復心室中膈缺損<ref name=NIH2011Tx/>。若是嬰兒年紀太小，可先進行暫時性的手術並安排於較大時進行二次手術<ref name=NIH2011Tx>{{cite web|title=How Is Tetralogy of Fallot Treated?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/tof/treatment|website=NHLBI|accessdate=2 October 2016|date=July 1, 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005191332/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/tof/treatment|archivedate=5 October 2016|df=}}</ref>。大多數有此症的患者皆能存活至成年<ref name=NIH2011What/>。長期的問題可能包含[[心律不整|心律不整]]以及{{le|肺動脈瓣閉鎖不全|pulmonary regurgitation}}<ref name=War2005>{{cite journal|last1=Warnes|first1=Carole A.|title=The Adult With Congenital Heart Disease|journal=Journal of the American College of Cardiology|date=July 2005|volume=46|issue=1|pages=1–8|doi=10.1016/j.jacc.2005.02.083|pmid=15992627}}</ref>。

== 流行病學及歷史 ==
每兩千名新生兒中就有一例出現法洛氏四重症<ref name=NIH2011What/>，男嬰女嬰罹患機率相等<ref name=NIH2011What/>為最常見的複雜性先天性心臟病，約佔複雜性先天性心臟病的10%<ref>{{Cite book |title=Johns Hopkins textbook of cardiothoracic surgery |date=2014 |publisher=McGraw-Hill Companies |author=Yuh, David D. |isbn=9780071663502|edition=2nd |location=New York|oclc=828334087}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Types of Congenital Heart Defects|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/types|website=NHLBI|accessdate=2 October 2016|date=1 July 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005180430/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/chd/types|archivedate=5 October 2016|df=}}</ref>，1671年時，[[尼古拉斯·斯坦諾|尼古拉斯·斯坦諾]]第一次提到了法洛氏四重症<ref name=Name2016>{{cite web|title=Fallot's tetralogy|url=http://www.whonamedit.com/synd.cfm/2281.html|website=Whonamedit?|accessdate=2 October 2016|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003083817/http://www.whonamedit.com/synd.cfm/2281.html|archivedate=3 October 2016|df=}}</ref><ref name=VanP2009>{{cite journal |last1=Van Praagh |first1=R |title=The first Stella van Praagh memorial lecture: the history and anatomy of tetralogy of Fallot. |journal=Seminars in Thoracic and Cardiovascular Surgery. Pediatric Cardiac Surgery Annual |volume=12 |date=2009 |pages=19–38 |doi=10.1053/j.pcsu.2009.01.004 |pmid=19349011}}</ref>。1888年時由法國醫生{{le|艾蒂安-路易·亞瑟·法洛|Étienne-Louis Arthur Fallot}}做更進一步的描述，並因此得名<ref name=Name2016/><ref name=Fallot1888>{{Cite book|oclc=457786038|title=Contribution à l'anatomie pathologique de la maladie bleue (cyanose cardiaque), par le Dr. A. Fallot, ...|last=Fallot|first=Arthur|date=1888|publisher=Impr. de Barlatier-Feissat|isbn=|location=Marseille|pages=77–93|language=fr}}</ref>。於1954年，進行第一次的修復手術<ref name=War2005/>。 


